text:
- [Announcer] AWS Data
Exchange gives customers
an efficient way to find, subscribe to,
and use third party data in the cloud.

This fully managed
service simplifies access
to hundreds of diverse datasets,

including traditional market
data like company fundamentals,
pricing, and global reference data.

Less traditional data, such
as workforce composition,

consumer transactions, and
location data are also available.

You can integrate data
from AWS Data Exchange

with existing models to
more accurately forecast
asset price movements,

identify risks in your
investment portfolio,

and more quickly integrate
data-driven insights

into your trading, research,
and investment processes.
Subscribe to a data product and analyze it
using a wide variety of AWS analytics
and machine learning services.

Numerous data providers
offer flexible trials

so you can evaluate the
data before you buy.
You will also find hundreds

of free public data sources
to support your analysis.
Learn more and get started today.
